{"tid":2046131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"“反法”不單止騎劫了美國反黑警運動，還騎劫了香港抗爭運動…","createTime":"2020-06-01T08:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T11:40:10.000Z","uid":195252,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67bcc1a40012bfba3131573c9d0a0a748118a57c","tid":2046131,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"本身為左反黑警而燒警署同燒警車係可以理解。<br />\n<br />\n點知近排好多示威者個個都blackbloc走去大肆搶掠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由反黑警變成走去搶掠唔少美國人都開始反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後見到blackbloc，戴豬嘴既人都反感（包括香港示威者）&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n應該點算&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;反法&rdquo;是指反法西斯的意思<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8p0PUd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8p0PUd.png&h=1572d81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左=1933年威瑪共和國共產黨旗<br />\n右=2017年反法西斯旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1db5cdd4dfa33eb334bcbf5c90f73dbb1c6b6c","tid":2046131,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b4043c70763bde284072d3823bfb99ecc24c854f","tid":2046131,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"dd9647a91cd336201953b82921565b9178bb7661","tid":2046131,"uid":199957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"關撚事咩 我地冇LOOTING過 我地仲負責捉賊綁佢喺條電燈柱度 等狗放走佢"},{"pid":"aa99e4aa3f634412fcabd232cf9ea3d0aa1d36e9","tid":2046131,"uid":44298,"li